                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The cu sith has a Large or smaller creature grabbed in its jaws</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The cu sith viciously shakes its prey. The cu sith makes a jaws Strike against the grabbed creature with a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll. If the cu sith hits, it deals jaws damage, maintains its Grab, and attempts an Athletics check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Disarm] its target of anything it is holding. On a miss, the cu sith releases the creature.</p>"
